title: MisterMusic Show 294 NEW indie,alternative,rock Radio
description:
MisterMusic Show 294    192kbps MP3 Stereo

A lot of new music featured on this episode of the MisterMusic Show.
New stuff by Elbow, We Are Scientists, Real Estate, Cymbals, Broken Bells,
and The Pixies.

And we travel back musically, to March 1989 for a number 1 hit on the modern and
album rock charts 25 years ago, for the 'Oldie Of The Week'.


It is a blend of new indie, alternative music with over 5 decades of classic tunes.
The MisterMusic Show is broadcast weekly and heard globally on Rock XS Radio.

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------

For recorded podcasts of the MisterMusic show, visit his podcast page http://mistermusicshow.com
Shows are updated there first every Sunday.
Or you can google search  mistermusicshow  (spelled as one word) and you'll find it.
